title: True Grit Ride
description: A ride to benefit the Community Services Clearinghouse, 10 Mile Family Fun Ride and 35, 50 and 100 Mile Routes.

directions: Ben Geren Park is located on Zero Street (Hwy 255) due south of the airport in Fort Smith.

title: Mt Gaylor Time Trail/Arkansas State Hill Climb
Hazel Valley Grand Prix
course: 50 miles all on dirt roads. 5000 ft of elevation gain.
directions:
From Fayetteville; Take Hwy 16 East past ELKINS to DURHAM (about 14 miles) and …. Look for the “TERRA STUDIOS” 
sign and… Turn RIGHT on HAZEL VALLEY ROAD (county road 47) Go about 6 miles & (be sure to go DOWNHILL on 
pavement at a tight 180 degree turn)… The pavement will end at the bottom of the hill at a “T” intersection… GO LEFT for 
approx 200yds (Olive rd.), and look LEFT for “16330” on the mailbox… Pull up the driveway and there should be several 
people around… Pitch tents BEHIND the main lodge & around the grassy areas.
